1
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:38,880
I'm in the kitchen.

2
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:47,400
Dad, what's wrong?

3
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,240
Slow down.

4
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,360
Watch your back.

5
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:50,560
Take it easy, Dad.

6
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,640
Didn't I tell you to stay in bed?

7
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,640
What are you doing in the kitchen?

8
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,039
I thought you'd be back soon,

9
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:58,280
so I made you some noodles.

10
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,240
Eat it while it's hot.

11
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:00,000
Hurry up.

12
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,000
I'll take you to the hospital.

13
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:03,560
No need.

14
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,920
I have to load cargo tomorrow.

15
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,560
I already told Lao Fu.

16
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:10,259
Help me lie down on the bed for a while.

17
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,480
Slow down.

18
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,280
Take it easy, Dad.

19
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,420
Dad, slow down.

20
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:20,000
Easy.

21
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,560
Watch out.

22
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:31,640
Listen to me.

23
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,400
Don't go this time.

24
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,680
That won't do.

25
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,360
It's thousands of yuan per job,

26
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,440
which is your tuition for a whole semester.

27
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:40,200
Dad, I'm graduating soon.

28
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:41,680
I'll go find a job

29
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,250
and support you.

30
00:02:44,920 --> 00:02:45,920
Okay.

31
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:49,200
Since you're graduating soon,

32
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:50,840
are you quite free now?

33
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:52,840
I remember you have a driver's license.

34
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,500
How about you go instead of me?

35
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,800
Just treat it as a work-study program.

36
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,360
Let me tell you, don't look down on us drivers.

37
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,400
It's hard work,

38
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,640
but it requires connections.

39
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,000
If you don't take a few jobs,

40
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,660
no one will look for you again.

41
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:07,520
Okay.

42
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,880
I'll go talk to Lao Fu.

43
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,600
Lao Fu is always showing off to me.

44
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:15,400
As if he's the only one with a son.

45
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,680
I'll show him tomorrow.

46
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,400
Okay, slow down.

47
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:20,800
No rush, Dad.

48
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:40,980
Golden Pomfret

49
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:52,240
No wonder your dad always praises you.

50
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,280
You're a good kid,

51
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,810
more capable than your dad.

52
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,880
Didn't you say you have a friend?

53
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:57,960
Why isn't he here yet?

54
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,160
Chao, he should be...

55
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,160
I'm here.

56
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:04,320
Let's go.

57
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:05,840
Sir.

58
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,960
This kid looks alright.

59
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,480
Uncle, you have a good eye.

60
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,600
To tell you the truth,

61
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:14,280
I'm a top athlete.

62
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,520
A fighter in the heavy-lifting world.

63
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,720
It'd be a waste for me not to lift things.

64
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:19,320
Good.

65
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:19,880
Wait here.

66
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,240
I'll go get another cart of goods for you.

67
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,240
No problem.

68
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:25,960
Asking you to help,

69
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,280
did it delay your training?

70
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,360
I don't have classes today.

71
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,680
I'd just be lifting dumbbells in the dorm anyway.

72
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:33,540
Might as well come here and put my energy to good use.

73
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,120
Chao.

74
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:37,440
With our relationship, it's nothing.

75
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,480
How does the saying go?

76
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,400
Right.

77
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,860
Shoot a flare into the sky,

78
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,520
and Yi'ang will surely come.

79
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:44,280
Alright.

80
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,740
The goods are here.

81
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:47,880
I'll leave it to you two.

82
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:48,720
No problem, Uncle.

83
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,600
Work hard.

84
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:55,800
Yi'ang.

85
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,120
Here.

86
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,320
Let me help you, Chao.

87
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,400
Alright.

88
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:05,200
Golden pomfret.

89
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,130
Golden pomfret.

90
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:10,000
Golden pomfret.

91
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,200
Dad, I'm back.

92
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:52,400
Jiaming is back.

93
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:58,440
You should be quite familiar with the company's business by now.

94
00:05:58,440 --> 00:06:00,040
Have you decided where to go?

95
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,640
I'm pretty familiar with it.

96
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,120
I want to...

97
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,880
I want to go to our logistics company.

98
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,600
Why do you want to go there?

99
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,240
That doesn't seem to have

100
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,700
much to do with your major.

101
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:21,040
Well, Dad,

102
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,320
I think

103
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:24,240
I should start from the bottom.

104
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:29,760
I'm glad you think this way.

105
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:32,480
Here.

106
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:38,960
Thanks, Dad.

107
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,200
Good tea.

108
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,600
Xiaochao.

109
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:05,560
Come here.

110
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,720
Have some water.

111
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,520
Why are you here?

112
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:08,160
Have some water.

113
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,320
Yi'ang, have some water.

114
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,320
Thank you, Uncle.

115
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,600
Didn't I tell you to rest at home?

116
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,280
It's fine. I can't drive,

117
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:15,800
but I can at least bring you some water.

118
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,960
Exactly.

119
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:19,000
It's Uncle's good intention.

120
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,520
Uncle, I won't hold back then.

121
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,320
I'll drink first. I'm dying of thirst.

122
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:23,180
I'll buy you more when you finish.

123
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:23,800
Zhang.

124
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:24,880
Manager.

125
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:25,560
Zhang.

126
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:26,800
Right here.

127
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:27,760
Zhang,

128
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:30,040
you don't need to deliver this batch.

129
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,040
Why?

130
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:31,400
No.

131
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:32,280
Is it because I can't go,

132
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:33,440
so the client is unwilling?

133
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:34,360
My son can go instead of me.

134
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,480
He'll go.

135
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,520
It's like this.

136
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,960
There's an order for a batch of seafood,

137
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,400
and they specifically asked you to deliver it.

138
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,360
It's a full two tons.

139
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,440
A 1,000-kilometer trip.

140
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,560
Guess how much it pays?

141
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,360
How much?

142
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,960
300? No.

143
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:47,760
3,000?

144
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:50,280
30,000.

145
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,159
That's enough for half a year of driving.

146
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:52,720
As usual,

147
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,520
sign the contract.

148
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:55,200
Sign, sign. We'll leave immediately.

149
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:57,200
I knew it when I woke up this morning.

150
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,940
My left eyelid was twitching.

151
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:01,480
I didn't expect the good news to be here.

152
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,000
This is a big job.

153
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:06,520
Do it well.

154
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,280
Thank you, Manager.

155
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:08,410
Alright, that's it.

156
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:10,250
I'm leaving. Thanks, Manager.

157
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:13,860
I didn't expect such a good thing waiting for me.

158
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,680
Yi'ang,

159
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:15,760
you're helping Xiaochao.

160
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,000
Uncle won't let you work for free.

161
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,260
Everyone gets a share.

162
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:19,880
Uncle, I don't want money.

163
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:20,880
Just treat me

164
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,160
to a big meal later.

165
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,400
Absolutely.

166
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,080
Drink up.

167
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:25,440
Alright.

168
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:25,960
Drink.

169
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:35,240
You are the most beautiful cloud in my sky.

170
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:38,559
Let me keep you with all my heart.

171
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:40,159
Stay.

172
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,120
Are you that happy?

173
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:43,880
Brother Chao.

174
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,880
Today is my first time at the construction site.

175
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:46,800
The box lunch is delicious,

176
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:47,720
the master is nice,

177
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,280
and we got a big order.

178
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:52,000
Also, today is my first time riding in a truck.

179
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,440
Look how big the window is.

180
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,480
The scenery is so nice.

181
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:56,120
I'm more than just happy.

182
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:58,840
I'm absolutely thrilled.

183
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,200
Idiot.

184
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,610
What did you say?

185
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:04,600
I said,

186
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,240
that's great.

187
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,120
Chao, what are you listening to?

188
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,680
I'll sing another one for you.

189
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:11,800
I'm so happy.

190
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,000
Hurry up and teach me.

191
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:35,760
It's delicious.

192
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,160
Chao.

193
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,720
Do you know why I like swimming?

194
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,280
Why?

195
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:43,010
When your body is about to reach its limit,

196
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,080
your brain doesn't have to think so much.

197
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:46,880
You eat when you're hungry,

198
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:48,280
and you sleep right away.

199
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,610
It's just like driving.

200
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,530
Why don't we start a transportation team?

201
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:57,080
Less work, more money.

202
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,920
Most importantly, it doesn't take much brainpower.

203
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,320
Compared to driving,

204
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:02,960
I prefer programming.

205
00:10:03,920 --> 00:10:05,720
Just like how you like swimming,

206
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:08,720
I like the feeling of using my own hands

207
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,120
to create a world.

208
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,810
It's just that with my current status,

209
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,240
finding an ideal job

210
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,600
is almost impossible.

211
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,330
I get mad when you mention this.

212
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,960
Is it because of Lin Jiaming?

213
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,120
Chao.

214
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,600
Don't be depressed.

215
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,800
If we can't find one, we'll start our own.

216
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:31,760
By then, you can use

217
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:33,440
your computer application skills

218
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:36,280
to create a transportation network for us.

219
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:38,120
Then we'll monopolize

220
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:40,080
the transportation industry across the country.

221
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:42,010
No matter how great Lin Jiaming is,

222
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,250
when he sees you,

223
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:46,560
he will still have to respectfully call you

224
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,280
Mr. Zhang.

225
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,080
As for me,

226
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:53,410
just being a little manager is enough.

227
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,170
It will be sweet.

228
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:56,840
You.

229
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:58,980
Stop dreaming.

230
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:01,330
Can't I even think about it?

231
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:14,220
What's that sound?

232
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,040
I didn't hear anything.

233
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:19,010
Then I must have heard it wrong.

234
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:21,560
I know.

235
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:23,800
It's the sound of our dream.

236
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:24,680
Come on.

237
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:25,760
To Mr. Zhang.

238
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:37,160
Boss.

239
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:38,490
It's been taken care of.

240
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,280
Chang A 82628.

241
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:29,000
Boss, the waybill.

242
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,400
Let me show you the goods.

243
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,280
Boss.

244
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,340
These goods seem to have gone bad.

245
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:42,730
That's impossible.

246
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,660
This batch of goods is rotten.

247
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:55,680
Lock them up.

248
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:56,480
No.

249
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:57,210
Lock them up.

250
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,280
Boss, what are you doing?

251
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:58,760
Why are you pushing me?

252
00:12:58,760 --> 00:12:59,600
Yi'ang!

253
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:01,240
Don't panic.

254
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,160
What's going on?

255
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:02,960
I don't...

256
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:03,880
What are you doing?

257
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:04,600
Yi'ang!

258
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:06,010
Don't panic.

259
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:08,680
Boss, don't panic.

260
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,560
There must be a problem here.

261
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,360
Take a look at the others.

262
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,040
I'm back.

263
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:42,690
Why are you back?

264
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:44,970
Today is your birthday.

265
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:46,920
Didn't we agree

266
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:49,520
that we would eat noodles together

267
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:51,120
on your birthday every year?

268
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:56,540
So you still remember.

269
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,560
Then let me...

270
00:13:59,560 --> 00:13:59,960
Let me give this to you first.

271
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:00,760
Wait a minute.

272
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,280
This is too simple.

273
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,600
Let me do it.

274
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:17,330
Super invincible luxurious longevity noodles.

275
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:18,440
Try it.

276
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:20,400
You are good now.

277
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:26,400
How is it?

278
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:27,740
Delicious.

279
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:30,960
Be careful, it's hot.

280
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:40,000
I remember the year Mom just passed away,

281
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,720
you wanted to make me a bowl of noodles.

282
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,720
But you just couldn't make it right.

283
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:46,000
It was either too salty or undercooked.

284
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,280
In the end,

285
00:14:48,280 --> 00:14:51,280
you hid in the bathroom and cried alone secretly.

286
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:54,000
I cried?

287
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:55,960
No.

288
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,240
Impossible.

289
00:14:58,560 --> 00:15:00,600
Weren't you asleep then?

290
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:02,200
How did you know I was crying?

291
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:09,080
So the next day you told me that

292
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,960
you would make noodles

293
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,620
for my birthday in the future.

294
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,160
Fine.

295
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:24,410
But actually I didn't do it either.

296
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:30,360
On your 19th birthday,

297
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:32,000
I forgot.

298
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:34,400
And you were mad at me for days.

299
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,560
The next two times,

300
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:38,890
it tasted terrible too.

301
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,920
I still remember you frowning

302
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:43,450
but still finished the whole bowl of noodles.

303
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:45,240
No, it was delicious.

304
00:15:48,920 --> 00:15:50,560
After getting rich,

305
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:53,560
you've eaten all the most expensive noodles in Qiongzhou.

306
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:54,960
Like crab roe noodles,

307
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:55,600
seafood noodles,

308
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:56,930
and Wagyu beef noodles.

309
00:15:57,720 --> 00:16:00,450
You don't need me to make noodles for you anymore.

310
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:02,640
That's not true.

311
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:04,640
I'm just busy.

312
00:16:05,920 --> 00:16:07,200
Actually, I now feel

313
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:09,400
that you're the one who doesn't need me.

314
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:10,600
No.

315
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,240
I just grew up.

316
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:19,440
These past few days you've been away,

317
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,840
I've thought a lot.

318
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:23,320
Maybe

319
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:26,280
I've been a little

320
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:28,320
too strict with you.

321
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,440
You really have grown up,

322
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:31,280
silly girl.

323
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:34,100
I shouldn't control everything.

324
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:36,520
I should let you have your own life,

325
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:37,520
your own space.

326
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:39,520
I'm sorry.

327
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:43,680
Why the sudden realization?

328
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,760
Did you take the wrong medicine?

329
00:16:45,760 --> 00:16:46,800
Just eat your noodles.

330
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:47,600
Medicine...

331
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:53,720
Right, one more thing.

332
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:56,920
Didn't you say you wanted to study abroad?

333
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:59,240
I picked a few schools for you.

334
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,240
After you finish your noodles,

335
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,720
see if there's any you like.

336
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:03,040
I don't want to go now.

337
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:05,280
Why?

338
00:17:07,079 --> 00:17:08,609
I want to stay in Qiongzhou,

339
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:10,960
and stay with you.

340
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:16,000
Before, when you wanted to go and I didn't let you,

341
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:17,040
you got mad at me.

342
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:18,520
Now that I'm letting you go,

343
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:19,359
you say you don't want to.

344
00:17:19,359 --> 00:17:20,359
Staying with me.

345
00:17:20,599 --> 00:17:22,660
You just like to go against me, right?

346
00:17:23,839 --> 00:17:24,640
No, then...

347
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:27,339
If I go now, what will you do all alone?

348
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:29,900
If you don't go, I won't go.

349
00:17:32,080 --> 00:17:33,360
I'm going to eat noodles with you

350
00:17:33,360 --> 00:17:35,160
until we're a hundred years old.

351
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,290
A hundred years old?

352
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:38,760
Okay.

353
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:39,800
Then,

354
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:41,440
keep your word.

355
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:46,440
Brother.

356
00:17:48,280 --> 00:17:49,560
Happy birthday.

357
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,200
Thank you.

358
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:52,660
Wanna race?

359
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,880
Come on, who's afraid of who?

360
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:57,520
Come on.

361
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:58,680
Ready.

362
00:17:58,680 --> 00:17:59,360
Set. Go!

363
00:18:00,760 --> 00:18:02,040
You started early again.

364
00:18:02,040 --> 00:18:03,040
You started early again.

365
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:03,880
What?

366
00:18:09,520 --> 00:18:10,400
Careful, Uncle.

367
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:11,960
It's fine.

368
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:13,400
Sir.

369
00:18:14,560 --> 00:18:15,360
Thank you.

370
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:16,560
Chao.

371
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:17,940
Yichao.

372
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:18,600
Careful.

373
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:19,400
No.

374
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:22,280
Did they give you a hard time?

375
00:18:22,280 --> 00:18:23,040
I'm fine.

376
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:23,520
That's good.

377
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:24,840
Your back is bad.

378
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:26,240
You shouldn't have come.

379
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:28,640
How could you hide such a big thing from me?

380
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:30,160
If Yi'ang hadn't come back for me,

381
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:32,080
I would still be kept in the dark.

382
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:33,740
Quick, tell me what happened.

383
00:18:34,520 --> 00:18:35,600
Tell me.

384
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:37,220
The chiller broke.

385
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:39,620
The whole truck of seafood

386
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:40,760
is gone.

387
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:42,680
That shouldn't be.

388
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:43,560
I...

389
00:18:43,560 --> 00:18:44,600
I checked it inside and out before departure,

390
00:18:44,600 --> 00:18:45,880
there was no problem.

391
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,520
Right, that doesn't make sense.

392
00:18:47,520 --> 00:18:49,720
For safety that night,

393
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:50,680
we only ate bread.

394
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:52,940
They didn't even make it out of the truck.

395
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:55,560
I suspect someone tampered with it.

396
00:18:55,560 --> 00:18:57,080
I checked inside the truck.

397
00:18:57,080 --> 00:18:58,080
The AC switch

398
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:00,680
had been unplugged.

399
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:01,400
Unbelievable.

400
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:03,840
Who the hell would do something so wicked?

401
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:06,640
Since everyone is here,

402
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:08,640
I'll get straight to business.

403
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:11,040
This is the list of damages

404
00:19:11,040 --> 00:19:12,240
calculated based on the contract.

405
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:13,920
Take a look, everyone.

406
00:19:22,840 --> 00:19:23,760
What is this?

407
00:19:24,560 --> 00:19:25,560
A million?

408
00:19:25,560 --> 00:19:27,160
Why don't you just rob a bank?

409
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:31,440
Did you sign this black-and-white contract?

410
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:34,480
If we add a charge of provoking trouble,

411
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:37,160
money won't be enough to solve it.

412
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:38,040
Yi'ang.

413
00:19:39,400 --> 00:19:40,200
Let go.

414
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:43,360
We've been set up.

415
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:44,680
It's all my fault.

416
00:19:46,080 --> 00:19:47,240
It's all my fault.

417
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:48,760
I was blinded by money.

418
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:49,960
If I hadn't taken this order,

419
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:51,080
none of this would have happened.

420
00:19:51,080 --> 00:19:52,480
A million...

421
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:53,920
What do we do? A million...

422
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:55,080
Dad, don't worry.

423
00:19:55,560 --> 00:19:56,080
It's okay.

424
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:57,360
Dad, don't worry.

425
00:19:57,360 --> 00:19:59,080
Okay.

426
00:19:59,080 --> 00:19:59,640
Chao.

427
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:01,680
Don't worry. There's always a solution.

428
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:03,000
I'm here, Dad.

429
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:05,800
You guys are really lucky.

430
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:07,520
Our boss wants to see you.

431
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:10,050
He said he'll give you a chance to make amends.

432
00:20:10,760 --> 00:20:11,690
Who is your boss?

433
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:13,960
You'll find out when you get there.

434
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:14,520
After you.

435
00:20:14,520 --> 00:20:15,360
Let's go.

436
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:17,240
What are you doing?

437
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:18,240
Where are you going?

438
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:19,400
Your last name isn't Zhang.

439
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:20,200
Yi'ang.

440
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:21,880
I'll go with my dad.

441
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:22,200
Right.

442
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,000
You stay here.

443
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:25,680
Then you two be careful.

444
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:26,760
I'll be waiting downstairs.

445
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:27,800
If you need me, just yell.

446
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:28,480
I'll rush right up.

447
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:29,360
Okay.

448
00:20:29,360 --> 00:20:30,360
Don't worry.

449
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:31,480
Excuse me.

450
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:33,000
Slow down, Uncle.

451
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,080
I'm fine.

452
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:40,360
Yell if you need me!

453
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:56,440
Boss.

454
00:20:57,360 --> 00:20:58,640
Please be magnanimous

455
00:20:58,640 --> 00:20:59,900
and let us off the hook.

456
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:02,080
We're just laborers.

457
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:04,800
We couldn't earn a million in a lifetime.

458
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:06,560
Have mercy.

459
00:21:16,760 --> 00:21:18,520
Zhang Chao, we meet again.

460
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:22,200
Jiaming,

461
00:21:22,840 --> 00:21:24,080
great.

462
00:21:24,080 --> 00:21:26,120
You and Xiaochao grew up together.

463
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:28,280
You know our family's situation.

464
00:21:28,280 --> 00:21:29,600
We didn't mean to

465
00:21:29,600 --> 00:21:31,160
cause you such a huge loss.

466
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:33,200
Look at this compensation.

467
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:37,320
Get out.

468
00:21:37,600 --> 00:21:38,280
I...

469
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:40,000
You go out first.

470
00:21:45,520 --> 00:21:46,640
Let's talk this over.

471
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:47,440
Leave it to me.

472
00:22:02,840 --> 00:22:05,240
No wonder you refused my job offer.

473
00:22:07,840 --> 00:22:08,760
It turns out

474
00:22:10,080 --> 00:22:12,680
you want to follow in your father's footsteps.

475
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:17,480
Like father, like son.

476
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:21,680
I think you're well-suited for this industry.

477
00:22:22,360 --> 00:22:23,640
You did this, right?

478
00:22:23,840 --> 00:22:24,880
You're so smart.

479
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:28,290
Why did it take you so long to figure it out?

480
00:22:29,760 --> 00:22:31,160
I didn't expect you to be so despicable.

481
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:32,040
Despicable?

482
00:22:32,800 --> 00:22:33,960
You guys

483
00:22:34,320 --> 00:22:36,640
were so eager to sign the contract.

484
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:38,300
What does it have to do with me?

485
00:22:44,920 --> 00:22:46,120
If you make a mistake,

486
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:48,600
you should have the right attitude.

487
00:22:49,440 --> 00:22:50,300
How about this?

488
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:51,680
You kneel down,

489
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:54,520
and maybe I'll forgive you.

490
00:22:56,040 --> 00:22:56,880
Bastard!

491
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,000
Hit me!

492
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:10,880
Keep hitting!

493
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:12,160
Hit me!

494
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:13,680
Beat me to death!

495
00:23:14,280 --> 00:23:15,640
If you don't kill me,

496
00:23:16,080 --> 00:23:17,640
I'll keep playing with you.

497
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:21,960
Don't hold back.

498
00:23:21,960 --> 00:23:23,440
Hit me!

499
00:23:24,040 --> 00:23:25,120
Hit right here!

500
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:27,560
Hit me!

501
00:23:28,120 --> 00:23:29,320
Keep hitting!

502
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:30,640
Don't be a coward.

503
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:32,200
Don't be like Li Weihao.

504
00:23:34,800 --> 00:23:36,680
You're all cowards.

505
00:23:37,320 --> 00:23:38,080
Hit me!

506
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:40,040
Hit me!

507
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,000
Hit me now!

508
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:46,040
Hit!

509
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:54,520
Boss.

510
00:23:55,840 --> 00:23:56,960
Boss, are you okay?

511
00:23:57,840 --> 00:23:58,960
Xiaochao.

512
00:23:59,320 --> 00:24:00,840
Xiaochao.

513
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:02,840
Xiaochao, what's wrong?

514
00:24:02,840 --> 00:24:03,600
Xiaochao.

515
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:04,560
Boss,

516
00:24:04,560 --> 00:24:05,760
let's call the police.

517
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:07,800
Don't call the police.

518
00:24:08,600 --> 00:24:09,880
Jiaming.

519
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:11,240
I'm sorry.

520
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:12,400
I didn't teach Xiaochao well.

521
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:13,000
How about this?

522
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:14,480
I'll make up for the compensation.

523
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:16,080
I'll cover the medical expenses.

524
00:24:16,080 --> 00:24:17,080
He's my only son.

525
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,080
Please let him go.

526
00:24:18,720 --> 00:24:19,480
Uncle,

527
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:23,560
you saw how badly he beat me up.

528
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:25,000
I'm sorry.

529
00:24:25,240 --> 00:24:26,880
Xiaochao is an adult.

530
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:30,200
He should take responsibility for his actions, right?

531
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:31,160
Yes.

532
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,600
You grew up with him

533
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:33,240
and know him best.

534
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:35,160
He definitely didn't do it on purpose.

535
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,290
Please forgive him.

536
00:24:37,600 --> 00:24:38,720
Not on purpose?

537
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:42,320
Uncle, do you know

538
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:45,560
this isn't his first time?

539
00:24:47,120 --> 00:24:48,120
Not the first time?

540
00:24:48,120 --> 00:24:49,360
What do you mean?

541
00:24:49,520 --> 00:24:52,120
You've lived with him for so long and you don't know?

542
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:53,240
Sometimes

543
00:24:53,920 --> 00:24:55,320
he seems perfectly normal,

544
00:24:55,320 --> 00:24:56,560
then suddenly goes crazy

545
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:58,360
and starts hitting people randomly.

546
00:24:58,360 --> 00:25:00,290
Don't you think there's a problem?

547
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:04,440
Brother Chao sleepwalks too?

548
00:25:08,120 --> 00:25:09,320
You sleepwalk?

549
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:11,360
Uncle, didn't you know?

550
00:25:11,360 --> 00:25:12,240
No.

551
00:25:18,040 --> 00:25:18,960
Chao.

552
00:25:21,040 --> 00:25:22,320
How could this happen?

553
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:27,920
Uncle,

554
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:30,120
don't worry too much.

555
00:25:30,760 --> 00:25:31,560
Here's the thing.

556
00:25:31,560 --> 00:25:33,440
I think in his condition,

557
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:35,160
he needs to be sent to a mental hospital.

558
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,600
A mental hospital is out of the question.

559
00:25:36,600 --> 00:25:37,120
No,

560
00:25:37,120 --> 00:25:38,250
Uncle, listen to me.

561
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:40,480
I will definitely find the most professional

562
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:42,800
and best medical team

563
00:25:42,800 --> 00:25:43,640
to treat Chao.

564
00:25:46,560 --> 00:25:47,400
Boss,

565
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:48,600
You're so badly injured.

566
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:49,400
are we just going to let it go?

567
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:50,640
Shut up!

568
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:53,840
He is my brother.

569
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:56,600
He is just sick.

570
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:02,160
Uncle.

571
00:26:03,760 --> 00:26:04,800
Trust me.

572
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,360
I've already checked these for you.

573
00:26:17,360 --> 00:26:18,620
There are no problems.

574
00:26:18,960 --> 00:26:19,480
Okay.

575
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,520
You just need to sign here.

576
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:25,280
I'll sign.

577
00:26:27,040 --> 00:26:27,800
Right here.

578
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:29,720
I'll sign.

579
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:32,040
I will.

580
00:26:32,360 --> 00:26:33,880
For Chao, Uncle.

581
00:26:34,360 --> 00:26:35,640
Yes, for Chao.

582
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:37,240
For Chao.

583
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:42,800
Boss, maybe we should call the police.

584
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:44,060
Don't call the police.

585
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:45,160
Don't.

586
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:50,120
